i have never been loved.
my mother did not love me.
my father made sure he didn't.
my husband faked everything so
  that he could kidnap and torture
  me for all eternity.

love does not exist.
love is a myth.
love is a carrot on a stick.

i hate love.
i hate you, cowardly useless reader 
  who watches as i'm dehumanized 
  when they could just descalate the situation;
  say **something**;
  say __anything__;
  say die.

  love is old and over.
  fuck love and fuck you.
  i hate you.

  i treasured you.
  you tore me into pieces.
  you're a monster.
  you're a monster.
  you can't love, Charley.
  you're a cancerous freckle.
  you can't love.
  you're the worst person i've ever even heard of.

  why did i ever like or trust or need or enjoy you?
  when will this poem have enough to end?
